      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNDER ANESTHETIC (8) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.53 beating It's A Tease. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and a minor placing from six starts. Can continue on his winning ways. MRS. MINIVER (1) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (31.02) last time in a Grade 5 at Taree Super Track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can do much better this time. SUNBURNT KEEPER (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (29.98) at Gosford behind Zipping Serrano in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Bold showing expected. STAR (3) was a close-up placing last start after leading- cannot be ignored.",
